# Admin Assets

This directory contains the production build output from Vite.

## Important

**Do not edit files in this directory directly.**

These files are generated by `npm run admin:build` and will be overwritten on each build.

## Source

The source code is in the `admin-ui/` directory at the project root.

## Contents

- JavaScript bundles (minified)
- CSS bundles (minified)
- Source maps for debugging
